An array is used for object management.

You can make an array by typing on the keyboard ex: 
    public ArrayList<Item> stuff = new ArrayList();
An ArrayList is a array that extends beyond just one use of the array.

An array is for singlular uses while arraylist extends to a much more numerus uses.
